{"thag2.11:0.1":"Theragatha 2.11 ","thag2.11:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.11:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","thag2.11:0.4":"Mahacundattheragatha ","thag2.11:1.1":"“Sussusa sutavaddhani, ","thag2.11:1.2":"sutam pannaya vaddhanam; ","thag2.11:1.3":"Pannaya attham janati, ","thag2.11:1.4":"nato attho sukhavaho. ","thag2.11:2.1":"Sevetha pantani senasanani, ","thag2.11:2.2":"Careyya samyojanavippamokkham; ","thag2.11:2.3":"Sace ratim nadhigaccheyya tattha, ","thag2.11:2.4":"Sanghe vase rakkhitatto satima”ti. ","thag2.11:2.5":"… Mahacundo thero …. "}